<p>

To understand the significance of Tonalli Wallet within the xolosArmy ecosystem, one must first analyze the technological substrate on which it operates: the <b>eCash blockchain</b>.

eCash is a Layer-1 network designed for fast digital cash transactions while preserving the security guarantees of Bitcoin's Proof-of-Work model.

</p>

